---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/layout/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/layout/Footer.astro';
import Button from '../components/ui/Button.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | Still">
  <Header />
  
  <main class="pt-32">
    <!-- Hero Section: Origin Story -->
    <section class="px-6 md:px-12 max-w-[1440px] mx-auto mb-32">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-center">
            <div class="md:col-span-7 animate-on-scroll">
                <span class="font-label text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-secondary mb-6 block">Our Origin</span>
                <h1 class="font-headline text-5xl md:text-7xl leading-[1.1] mb-12 text-on-surface">
                    The Art of <br/>
                    <span class="italic font-normal text-primary">Architectural Restraint</span>
                </h1>
                <div class="font-body text-lg md:text-xl text-secondary leading-relaxed max-w-2xl space-y-6">
                    <p>
                        Still was born from a singular observation: while physical wedding stationery had evolved into a high-art form, its digital counterpart remained trapped in generic templates and cluttered interfaces. 
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Founded as a specialized digital studio by the creative minds at <a href="https://massion.io" rel="nofollow" class="text-primary hover:underline">Massion Digital</a>, we set out to bridge the gap between the tactile beauty of traditional invitations and the effortless utility of modern technology. We believe your digital presence should feel as intentional and timeless as a hand-pressed card.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="md:col-span-5 animate-on-scroll" style="transition-delay: 200ms;">
                <div class="aspect-[4/5] bg-surface-container-low overflow-hidden rounded-sm border border-outline-variant/10 shadow-xl">
                    <img class="w-full h-full object-cover" data-alt="Bespoke studio portrait of our Creative Director in a minimalist, naturally lit architectural space" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDnRZU7nFqDksImJJIQNiqrkqIXhWnKRPrFKX9GSBt8WWwpd66GKeSWfOSMaiidu8R9UbQ2aztabDaEibDnrxBV-b3QmCcMa8vmvk8ll_rj2PxD0YmJYvX4Ldw2LbDqAYkgXGNb0rT_Cu-IALmVqzcS8CJ6clMdUqeZq1Fj3pqJ5nKvzbK-MTqf5SmCq4znx4Ua1SutEo-oAwCxsrhOi6vNwTOcCOaZAJfVCyz17FfZxz1W-fLhHtDuIcTiJ4VhwsC4ujDTJ6siAuDH"/>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Leadership Section -->
    <section class="bg-surface-container-low py-32 px-6 md:px-12 border-y border-outline-variant/10">
        <div class="max-w-[1440px] mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
             <div class="animate-on-scroll">
                <h2 class="font-headline text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-8 text-on-surface">Meet the <span class="italic text-primary">Director</span></h2>
                <div class="space-y-6">
                    <h3 class="font-headline text-2xl text-primary">Thomas Charisis</h3>
                    <p class="font-label text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-secondary">Founder & Creative Director</p>
                    <p class="font-body text-secondary text-lg leading-relaxed">
                        With a background in fine-art digital experiences at Massion Digital, Thomas founded Still to provide couples with a digital home that matches the caliber of their celebration. His philosophy is simple: technology should never shout; it should serve as a quiet, elegant witness to the story being told.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-surface p-12 rounded-sm shadow-sm border border-outline-variant/10 animate-on-scroll" style="transition-delay: 200ms;">
                <h3 class="font-headline text-2xl mb-8 text-on-surface italic">A Letter from the Studio</h3>
                <p class="font-body text-secondary leading-relaxed italic text-lg">
                    "We don't build websites; we commission digital heirlooms. In a world of 'fast-tech,' we choose architectural restraint. We choose the poetry of the slow scroll. We choose to make your guests feel the salt in the air or the warmth of the room before they even arrive."
                </p>
                <p class="mt-8 font-label text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-primary">— Still Studio Team</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Principles: Bento Grid -->
    <section class="py-32 px-6 md:px-12 max-w-[1440px] mx-auto">
        <div class="mb-16 animate-on-scroll">
            <span class="font-label text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-secondary mb-4 block">Our Principles</span>
            <h2 class="font-headline text-4xl md:text-5xl text-on-surface">How We <span class="italic text-primary">Work</span></h2>
        </div>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-6 md:gap-8">
            <!-- Principle 1: Detail -->
            <div class="md:col-span-6 bg-tertiary-container p-12 flex flex-col justify-center rounded-sm shadow-sm animate-on-scroll">
                <h3 class="font-headline text-3xl mb-6 text-on-tertiary-container italic">The 'Invisible' Detail</h3>
                <p class="font-body text-on-tertiary-container/80 leading-relaxed text-lg">
                    We obsess over the kerning of a headline and the ease of a mobile scroll. In luxury digital, the details you don't notice are the ones that create the most grace. If the technology feels invisible, we have succeeded.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Principle 2: Sophistication -->
            <div class="md:col-span-6 bg-surface-container-highest p-12 flex flex-col justify-center rounded-sm shadow-sm animate-on-scroll" style="transition-delay: 150ms;">
                <h3 class="font-headline text-3xl mb-6 text-on-surface italic">Digital as the New Paper</h3>
                <p class="font-body text-secondary leading-relaxed text-lg">
                    We treat a pixel with the same respect as a sheet of 600gsm cotton paper. This means avoiding the clutter of social feeds or generic widgets in favor of clean, architectural compositions and bespoke interaction.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Visual Anchor -->
            <div class="md:col-span-12 overflow-hidden rounded-sm shadow-sm animate-on-scroll group" style="transition-delay: 300ms;">
                <img class="w-full h-[500px] object-cover transition-transform duration-1000 group-hover:scale-105" data-alt="Close up of a refined digital interface mockup with hand-drawn typography and organic textures" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAmVNhgGULIHaxLFV8dmCA7CoI_dfgHpd_i072l74vljadGTyykv3tw6hux9H4-ZRcLGVUs7bkjC7Cp5xR77YXlaPwtgGhomkVgy23zDGIjvTYFD-Kqn4zse32SdjHTQr8MoySTCTrosdvFiGpeT2nwkEBFa6EpFUOE_MOOF8mPwMN3lWfxpNcViN3MTPNEJHd4fnJR2MZann1pvPXfz6LxXPckLjHLoYa5edzBhtDbwueMvipQgBSFmFCjwT03nTCcqkaixMegdqw0"/>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="py-32 px-6 md:px-12 bg-surface-container-low border-t border-outline-variant/10">
        <div class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto text-center animate-on-scroll">
            <h2 class="font-headline text-4xl md:text-6xl mb-12 text-on-surface">Experience the <span class="italic text-primary">Still</span> Standard</h2>
            <div class="flex justify-center">
                <Button href="/contact" variant="primary" class="px-12 py-4">Begin Your Commission</Button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>